## 3. Repository Structure

```
agentbus-skills/
├── README.md
├── scripts/
│   ├── write_plan.py        # write a plan file into a service repo
│   ├── read_plan.py         # read the latest (or specific) plan for current service
│   ├── list_services.py     # list registered services from config
│   ├── register_service.py  # register a service name + path
│   └── next_plan_number.py  # return next 3-digit plan index
└── skills/
    ├── agentbus-orchestrator/
    │   └── SKILL.md
    ├── agentbus-expert/
    │   └── SKILL.md
    └── map-codebase/
        └── SKILL.md
```

### Installation

```bash
# Global orchestrator (available in all projects)
npx skills add zentik/agentbus-skills --skill agentbus-orchestrator -g

# Per-project expert (run inside each service repo)
npx skills add zentik/agentbus-skills --skill agentbus-expert

# map-codebase is installed automatically as a dependency of the orchestrator
```

Works with Claude Code, Gemini CLI, Cursor, Codex, and any agent supporting the
[Agent Skills specification](https://agentskills.io).

