## 4. Prerequisites

### `uv`

All scripts require `uv`. The orchestrator skill checks for it before running any script.

**Check:**
```bash
uv --version
```

**Install if missing:**
```bash
curl -LsSf https://astral.sh/uv/install.sh | sh
```

No other global dependencies required.

