## 9. Failure Modes and Recovery

| Case | Expected behavior |
|---|---|
| Service not registered | Skip service, include in final report with reason `service-not-registered` |
| Docs unavailable | Trigger `map-codebase`, then continue with generated `AGENTS.md` on the corresponding service |
| Partial write failure | Keep successful service plans; report failures explicitly; no rollback |
| Existing plan refined twice | Update existing `## Expert Review` section in place |
| Invalid slug | Normalize to kebab-case or fail with clear validation error |

